HEADWORD: Leisurable
<hw>Lei"sur*a*ble</hw> <pr>(l⟦emac⟧"zh⟦usl⟧r*⟦adot⟧*b'l; 135)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Leisure</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Leisurely.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
